然后203 发表于 2013-12-31 21:46<br />
人文背景、教育背景、创业背景不一样。比如中国第一代创业者牟其中那样的，有可能在印度产生吗？<br />
<br />
不知道Reliance算不算。不知道你的标准哈。印度不少企业家都是白手起家的。可能比较注重资本市场吧。因为贷款难。印度贷款占gdp也就不到50%<br />
<br />
当然我不是说印度公司没问题。只是至少坑爹的时候比较有技术含量，而不是像一些国内公司连掩饰都不需要。可能说公司治理好有些不准确，说更专业些更好一些{:soso_e113:}<br />
<br />
下面是Reliance公司创始人在wiki上的介绍。真是个传奇。我那个原来混宝莱坞的哥们特佩服，虽然他个人更喜欢塔塔的风格。Reliance的故事，好的坏的好像非常多。现在哥俩貌似关系好一些了。<br />
<br />
Dhirubhai Ambani returned from Yemen to India and started &quot;Majin&quot; in partnership with Champaklal Damani, his second cousin, who lived with him in Aden, Yemen. Majin was to import polyester yarn and export spices to Yemen. The first office of the Reliance Commercial Corporation was set up at the Narsinatha Street in Masjid Bunder. It was a 350 sq ft (33 m2) room with a telephone, one table and three chairs. Initially, they had two assistants to help them with their business.<br />
<br />
by 2007 the combined fortune of the family was $60 billion, making the Ambanis the second richest family in the world. Ambani died on 6 July 2002				<p class="author">
